shop.title: Adorned Abode
shop.subtitle:
Here at Adorned Abode, we take tremendous pride in growing strong relationships with our customers. Giving someone a gift is a benevolent act of kindness. Our mission is to create a heartwarming experience when you shop with us. Selling a variety of goods, some locally made, fair trade items.

Supporting other small business is what we are all about. We hope to help you find the perfect gifts.
